    3472 [label="SPDXLicense:\nThis license is essentially a rebranded version of MPL-1.1, but with some\nimportant changes. The added §7.1 expands on the warranty disclaimer. The change\nin §11 moves the forum and the jurisdiction to Victoria, Australia (from\nCalifornia, USA in MPL-1.1). Section 3.7 of this license contains the word\n\"LEDs\" which appears to be a typo in the upstream version, at\nhttps://directory.fsf.org/wiki/License:NOSL. It is retained here as optional\ntext, so that it will still match in case others have used the license text with\nthis typo."
         ,fillcolor="beige;1"
         ,shape=plaintext];
